{"tid":1437682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我撐警既」 買左好撚多麵包生果可樂檸檬茶惠勞警察叔叔","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:49:22.000Z","uid":130898,"like":702,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"bc607b2884f81f7b20a136f4c00461d9a173a921","tid":1437682,"uid":130898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"今個星期六日 係你班仆街圍差館或者警察宿舍既時候<br />\n我會將一個個既麵包 生果 一包包既可樂 檸檬茶打開 <br />\n空投入差館同警察宿舍支持同惠勞警察叔叔<br />\n我勸你班仆街唔好撚再玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉投我地依面同我一齊一人一堆麵包生果可樂檸檬茶惠勞警察叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8a8bf0e9d943dc5458bc8d346e98c6fdae7fb3","tid":1437682,"uid":130898,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"淆底呀你班撚樣暴徒<br />\n投降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e95455eef5c20d513efa87677f80c62333683e","tid":1437682,"uid":8441,"like":128,"dislike":2,"score":126,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"食物留番俾前線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb292001a88d9e42b4b4c6ee6dd3f0bdd444da5","tid":1437682,"uid":273760,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"生命麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e760a1498ff4bf292c34b95b52ac6568c2b1b17f","tid":1437682,"uid":273716,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"凍撚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c386c96db16e9f0757c4b7eea8248da75416d7bf","tid":1437682,"uid":180589,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"唔好曬野食 佢地食狗糧嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79101fb6289c705a46a835118016eff69aeca91","tid":1437682,"uid":130898,"like":176,"dislike":0,"score":176,"quote":{"pid":"35e95455eef5c20d513efa87677f80c62333683e","tid":1437682,"uid":8441,"like":128,"dislike":2,"score":126,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"食物留番俾前線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"我屋企開雜貨鋪 <br />\n好多野飲就黎過期/冇人食冇人開<br />\n正好比我拎出黎惠勞警察叔叔<br />\n咁樣唔算賄賂啦 <br />\n你班撚樣暴徒想砌我地貪污<br />\n冇得傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1d9dc337edacf3bed4f94c2de7e6b6ff0e6bd2","tid":1437682,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"加料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66669f1c8e710033f131c47d44844a0a32be736c","tid":1437682,"uid":130898,"like":31,"dislike":5,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"你班撚樣 圍住差館同警察宿舍 <br />\n根本就同D蛇蟲鼠蟻一樣<br />\n比外國勢力既食物同飲品D野食引左過黎 <br />\n你地知唔知你地咁樣圍差館同警察宿舍 <br />\n好冇道德 <br />\n人地開工已經比你班暴徒屌 <br />\n返到屋企仲要因為污糟比老婆仔女屌 <br />\n有時訓訓下見到你班蛇蟲鼠蟻係屋企棟牆到<br />\n老婆仔女大叫大嗌點撚算<br />\n更加冇教好訓 <br />\n你班暴徒忍心咩"},{"pid":"851b542ebd26c9cc308d327e7edf728de9e52661","tid":1437682,"uid":130898,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"我決定帶埋D鹽糖油鼓油過去 <br />\n送比警嫂<br />\n支持佢地一直以黎撐住個警家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba03480f676ad280130ff88d2472067a2567dc4","tid":1437682,"uid":130898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"淆底呀你班撚樣暴徒<br />\n投降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c1fb278339c16201d5720e1820799380485bf7","tid":1437682,"uid":130898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc